# Rate-New Turborepo Workflow

## Core Commands
- **Start dev**: `yarn dev` từ root directory
- **Build project**: `yarn build` 
- **NEVER use npm**: Chỉ sử dụng yarn commands
- **PowerShell syntax**: Tránh bash commands

## Project Structure
- `apps/strapi/`: Strapi CMS backend với PostgreSQL
- `apps/ui/`: Next.js frontend
- `packages/`: Shared components và configs
- `Docs/`: Project documentation, guides, platform resources
  - `Docs/Modules/`: Module-specific documentation
  - `Docs/Guides/`: Development guides
  - `Docs/Platform/`: Platform documentation
  - `Docs/Resources/`: Additional resources
- `Modules/`: Core business modules
  - `Modules/Extension/`: Browser extension module với crawler
  - `Modules/Importer/`: Data import module với scripts
  - `Modules/Validator/`: Data validation module
- Luôn chạy commands từ D:\Projects\JOY\Rate

## Documentation Workflow
- **Check existing docs** trước khi tạo solutions mới
- **Reference Modules/** cho similar functionality patterns
- **Update Docs/** với new discoveries
- **Maintain consistency** với established patterns

## Development Rules  
- Kiểm tra port conflicts trước khi start
- Strapi admin: localhost:1337
- Next.js UI: localhost:3000



- Auto-restart services khi cần thiết